  "title": "Project Coordinator",
  "description": "<p>Job Summary:</p><p>The Interior Project Coordinator is responsible to oversee the renovation by providing on-site management, strategic plan, monitoring and adapting as needed. He/ she needs to interact confidently and build credible relationships with internal team members and external stakeholders.</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We’re looking for a systematic & meticulous Interior Project Coordinator to join our awesome team.</p><ul><li>Prepare ballpark, quotation, project timeline chart & proper document submission.</li><li>Provide technical advice and pre-empt potential challenges to Team & Client.</li><li>Manage manpower & resources to execute site works within the timeline</li><li>Responsible for initiating corrective actions & provide solutions to solve the site’s technical issues.</li><li>Carry out defects servicing of completed projects and maintain records of such servicing.</li><li>Update your residence/ commercial project progress to Project Director regularly.</li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Interior Design or equivalent</li><li>Candidates with 1 year of experience are preferred. However, entry-level candidates are also welcome</li><li>Basic project coordination and management are preferred</li><li>Basic software skills like AutoCAD/ Adobe Illustrator, MS Excel &PowerPoint should never be neglected.</li><li>Good communicator and eye for detail, systematic and good time management a HUGE bonus</li><li>Teamwork, motivation and self-empowerment</li><li>Willing to work in a fast-paced and challenging environment</li></ul><p><em>Interested applicant may click \"Apply\" for this role or send your resume to career@mrshopperstudio.com</em></p>",
